&lt;div data-qa=&quot;job-description&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;About The Role:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This isn’t just a recruiting role—it’s an opportunity to help build the company that’s redefining an entire industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a recruiter who is outstanding at the fundamentals—finding extraordinary talent, earning the attention of passive candidates, creating an exceptional candidate experience, and consistently closing high-impact hires. Beyond that, we’re looking for someone who thrives in the pace and ambiguity of an early-stage company and is excited to build alongside some of the brightest engineers, scientists, and business leaders in the industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll partner directly with hiring managers as a trusted advisor, helping shape hiring strategies, challenge assumptions, and influence decisions—not simply fill open roles. From defining the ideal candidate profile to sourcing, interviewing, and creating a thoughtful candidate experience, you’ll own the search end to end while helping build the teams that will shape the future of Atomic Machines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re energized by solving difficult hiring problems, working with brilliant people, and having a direct impact on a company that’s disrupting an entire industry, we’d love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
