&lt;p&gt;You will be the dedicated recruiter for our AIMS team — Artificial Intelligence, Modeling, and Simulation — a world-class research and engineering group working on some of the hardest problems in applied AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partnering with this team is not just a recruiting role; it is a front-row seat to how elite AI teams are built. You will own searches from intake through close, partnering closely with hiring managers to understand not only what each role requires, but what makes someone exceptional in it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will build sourcing strategies from scratch, craft outreach that earns responses from people who are not actively looking, and move candidates through a process that is transparent, efficient, and worth their time. When a search stalls, you will diagnose why and adjust. When a candidate has multiple competing offers, you will know how to keep them engaged and close effectively. You will keep hiring managers informed without overwhelming them, and you will push back when the bar drifts or the process breaks down.&lt;/p&gt;
